Result excerpt:

23/tcp  open  telnet


Version detection:

nmap -sV -p 23 192.168.56.101


Result:

23/tcp open telnet  Linux telnetd


âœ… Telnet is active and accepting remote logins.

ğŸ 2. Manual Access via Telnet

Attempting connection:

