âœ… We now have a remote shell as a valid system user.

ğŸš¨ Vulnerability Exploited

Protocol transmits all data in plaintext

Weak default credentials

No access restrictions

No encryption or authentication hardening

This represents a realâ€‘world misconfiguration often found in legacy environments.

ğŸ¯ 3. Privilege Escalation

Check sudo permissions:

